long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
ChatGPT can be incredibly dumb at times. This extension replaces the ChatGPT icon with a GIF of a silly cat. It makes ChatGPT slightly more tolerable when it messes up.

This extension is open source! Check out the source code here: https://github.com/JosephKan3/GPTuwu
